'''Umugezi wa Rukarara''' (cyangwa Lukarara) ni uruzi rwo mu [[Intara y'Uburengerazuba|burengerazuba]] bw'u [[Rwanda]]. ruturuka k' [[Umugezi wa Mwogo]], na rwo rukaba [[umugezi wa Nyabarongo]]. Namazi ava kure  cyane ya Nili. Rukarara izamuka ituruka m'amashyamba mu majyepfo y’u [[Rwanda]] mu burasirazuba bwa Congo-Nili.  Igishanga cya Kamiranzovu mu ishyamba rya Nyungwe ritanga ikigega gisanzwe cya Rukarara  Inkomoko ya Rukarara ubu izwiho kuba isoko rusange ya Nili  Ibi byashimangiwe n’urugendo rwa 2005/2006 ruzamuka uruzi rufite ibikoresho bigezweho. <ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rukarara_River</ref>

